[30;1m15 | [0m[35mFinally, it is infeasible to find two arbitrary messages with the[0m

[30;1m4 | [0m[35mDSA_ is a widespread public key signature algorithm. Its security is[0m
[30;1m5 | [0m[35mbased on the discrete logarithm problem (DLP_). Given a cyclic[0m
[30;1m6 | [0m[35mgroup, a generator *g*, and an element *h*, it is hard[0m
[30;1m7 | [0m[35mto find an integer *x* such that :math:`g^x = h`. The problem is believed[0m
[30;1m8 | [0m[35mto be difficult, and it has been proved such (and therefore secure) for[0m
[30;1m9 | [0m[35mmore than 30 years.[0m
[30;1m10 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m25 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m26 | [0m[35mA key object can be created in four ways:[0m
[30;1m27 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m28 | [0m[35m1. :func:`generate` at the module level (e.g. :func:`Crypto.PublicKey.RSA.generate`).[0m

       Tag: [34mSecurity.Backdoor.LOLBAS.Linux[0m
  Severity: [36mModerate[0m, Confidence: [36mLow[0m
  Filename: [33m/pycryptodome-3.22.0/Doc/src/public_key/elgamal.rst[0m
   Pattern: [32m\s(apt|apt\-get|aria2c|arp|ash|awk|base64|bash|bpftrace|busybox|cat|chmod|chown|cp|cpan|cpulimit|crontab|csh|curl|cut|dash|dd|diff|dmesg|dmsetup|dnf|docker|dpkg|easy_install|ed|emacs|env|expand|expect|facter|find|finger|flock|fmt|ftp|gawk|gdb|gimp|git|grep|head|iftop|ionice|ip|irb|jjs|journalctl|jrunscript|ksh|ld\.so|ldconfig|logsave|ltrace|lua|mail|mawk|mount|mtr|mv|mysql|nano|nawk|nc|nice|nl|nmap|node|od|openssl|perl|pg|php|pic|pico|pip|puppet|readelf|red|rlogin|rlwrap|rpm|rpmquery|rsync|ruby|run\-mailcap|run\-parts|rvim|scp|screen|script|sed|service|setarch|sftp|shuf|smbclient|socat|sort|sqlite3|ssh|start\-stop\-daemon|stdbuf|strace|systemctl|tail|tar|taskset|tclsh|tcpdump|tee|telnet|tftp|time|timeout|tmux|top|ul|unexpand|uniq|unshare|vi|vim|watch|wget|whois|wish|xargs|xxd|yum|zsh|zypper)\s[0m
[30;1m23 | [0m[35m--------------------[0m
[30;1m24 | [0m[35mThe security of the ElGamal encryption scheme is based on the computational[0m
[30;1m25 | [0m[35mDiffie-Hellman problem (CDH_). Given a cyclic group, a generator *g*,[0m
[30;1m26 | [0m[35mand two integers *a* and *b*, it is difficult to find[0m
[30;1m27 | [0m[35mthe element :math:`g^{ab}` when only :math:`g^a` and :math:`g^b` are known, and not *a* and *b*.[0m
[30;1m28 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m29 | [0m[35mAs before, the group is the largest multiplicative sub-group of the integers[0m
[30;1m30 | [0m[35mmodulo *p*, with *p* prime.[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m2981[0m[34m of [0m[33m3337[0m[31m ]--[0m

[30;1m10 | [0m[35m-------------------[0m
[30;1m11 | [0m[35mThe security of the ElGamal signature scheme is based (like DSA) on the discrete[0m
[30;1m12 | [0m[35mlogarithm problem (DLP_). Given a cyclic group, a generator *g*,[0m
[30;1m13 | [0m[35mand an element *h*, it is hard to find an integer *x* such that :math:`g^x = h`.[0m
[30;1m14 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m15 | [0m[35mThe group is the largest multiplicative sub-group of the integers modulo *p*,[0m
[30;1m16 | [0m[35mwith *p* prime.[0m

[30;1m9 | [0m[35m* *PureEdDSA*, where the message is signed directly.[0m
[30;1m10 | [0m[35m* *HashEdDSA*, where the message is first hashed, and only the resulting digest is signed.[0m
[30;1m11 | [0m[35m  This should only be used by streaming applications because it avoids double passes[0m
[30;1m12 | [0m[35m  on messages, at the cost of reduced collision resistance.[0m
[30;1m13 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m14 | [0m[35mThis module supports signatures for both variants (*PureEdDSA* and *HashEdDSA*),[0m
[30;1m15 | [0m[35mon the Ed25519 curve (with a 128-bit security level), and[0m

[30;1m1053 | [0m[35m* ``Crypto.Random`` stops being a userspace CSPRNG. It is now a pure wrapper over ``os.urandom``.[0m
[30;1m1054 | [0m[35m* Added certain resistance against side-channel attacks for GHASH (GCM) and DSA.[0m
[30;1m1055 | [0m[35m* More test vectors for ``HMAC-RIPEMD-160``.[0m
[30;1m1056 | [0m[35m* Update ``libtomcrypt`` headers and code to v1.17 (kudos to Richard Mitchell).[0m
[30;1m1057 | [0m[35m* RSA and DSA keys are checked for consistency as they are imported.[0m
[30;1m1058 | [0m[35m* Simplified build process by removing autoconf.[0m
[30;1m1059 | [0m[35m* Speed optimization to PBKDF2.[0m
